    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S-generation RX-7 is a superlative example of Mazda\u2019s longitudinal front-midship engineering. At its heart is a flawlessly maintained 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, exhibiting robust compression and a seamless transition between the primary and secondary Hitachi HT12 turbochargers. The power is delivered through a precise five-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis maintains its factory-spec 50/50 weight balance, with the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and power plant frame (PPF) showing no signs of fatigue or oxidation. The interior is free of the typical dash lifting or UV-induced brittle plastics, and the exterior retains its deep, factory-original luster. This is an investment-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast seeking mechanical purity.",
      "price": 45800.0,
