    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in its original, high-gloss factory paint with absolutely zero swirl marks, dings, or chips, this car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The interior remains in time-capsule condition, featuring supple leather seats with no bolster wear, pristine original floor mats, and a cabin that has never seen smoke or pets. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed strictly at the authorized dealership, with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. From the flawless alloy wheels wrapped in fresh premium rubber to the spotless engine bay, every inch of this vehicle reflects a life of meticulous care. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example of automotive excellence that looks, feels, and drives exactly as the manufacturer intended.",
